textAnnotations.description:
IT'S SAD THAT IT
TOOK THE DEATH
OF A BELOVED
PRESIDENT TO
MAKE IT HAPPEN.
IT'S GREAT TO SEE
OUR DIVIDED NATION
FINALLY COME
TOGETHER
GEORGE
H.w. BUSH
STATE
FUNERAL
